    "title": "Immediate Requirement Production Engineer at Adani Enterprises",
    "description": "We at Adani Enterprises are looking for an experienced Production Engineer based out of Vadodara. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Adani Enterprises:\nAdani Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in 5S\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Adani Enterprises!",
